% ðŸ”¹ Facts: diet(Disease, RecommendedDiet)
diet(diabetes, 'High fiber vegetables, whole grains, lean proteins, avoid sugar').
diet(hypertension, 'Low sodium diet, fresh fruits, vegetables, avoid processed food').
diet(obesity, 'Low calorie diet, more vegetables, lean protein, avoid junk food').
diet(anemia, 'Iron-rich foods like spinach, beans, meat, avoid tea/coffee').
diet(heart_disease, 'Low fat diet, whole grains, fish, avoid fried food').

% ðŸ”¹ Rule: suggest_diet/2
suggest_diet(Disease, Diet) :-
    diet(Disease, Diet).
